<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />When you see a thief, you agree with him;</para>

<para style="q1">you participate with those who commit adultery.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="19" style="v" />You give your mouth to evil,</para>

<para style="q1">and your tongue expresses deceit.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="20" style="v" />You sit and speak against your brother;</para>

<para style="q1">you slander your own mother's son.</para>
